WEBVTT

00:02.237 --> 00:03.370
I love you.

00:03.404 --> 00:05.105
But I can't be in
this relationship.

00:05.216 --> 00:07.217
So that's it, we're done?

00:07.252 --> 00:10.054
You are 19 having
your second baby.

00:10.088 --> 00:11.956
You have no job and you live
with your grandparents.

00:11.990 --> 00:15.326
Look, I love Niecy and I'm
gonna be there for her baby.

00:15.360 --> 00:18.028
I think they should come
live with me full-time.

00:18.063 --> 00:19.797
John is the better parent.

00:19.831 --> 00:22.499
There's a story breaking
about Terrence Mitchell

00:22.534 --> 00:24.435
involving the prison
exposé he wrote.

00:24.469 --> 00:26.470
Terrence is being
accused of journalistic fraud.

00:26.504 --> 00:28.806
Maybe I embellished
a few details.

00:28.840 --> 00:31.442
Everything you've accomplished
has been compromised.

00:31.476 --> 00:33.444
We did reach out to
Terrence Mitchell to come on

00:33.478 --> 00:35.370
and give his side of the
story, but he declined.

00:41.019 --> 00:42.886
Hey...
Niecy.

00:44.489 --> 00:45.889
Auntie.

00:45.924 --> 00:47.791
Look what I got.

00:47.826 --> 00:50.594
Yeah, I'm not really
into guilt gifts.

00:50.628 --> 00:53.464
Oh, come on, Niecy.

00:53.498 --> 00:55.132
Seriously?

00:57.135 --> 00:57.868
What?

00:57.902 --> 01:00.070
Remember this?

01:00.105 --> 01:02.206
Buying dresses for
Romero's wedding

01:02.240 --> 01:05.376
and you told me you
wanted to be a lawyer.

01:05.410 --> 01:08.078
You told me that you
wanted a house full of kids.

01:08.113 --> 01:10.748
Yeah, well, I got the house,
you got the kids.

01:18.723 --> 01:20.557
Calm down a little bit, quiet.

01:23.928 --> 01:27.965
I'm sorry I was being
so hard on you.

01:27.999 --> 01:30.067
You know, I just...

01:30.101 --> 01:33.437
I was wrong.

01:33.471 --> 01:35.172
I spent so much
time fussing at you

01:35.206 --> 01:36.540
about what you were gonna
do with your life,

01:36.574 --> 01:40.444
that I didn't take one
second to celebrate this baby

01:40.478 --> 01:43.080
and I'm sorry.

01:45.383 --> 01:49.286
Thank you.

01:49.320 --> 01:53.624
She wasn't a mistake, you know?

01:53.658 --> 01:55.526
You mean, you tried
to get pregnant?

01:55.560 --> 01:58.595
More like I didn't try not to.

01:59.898 --> 02:01.098
But Auntie...

02:01.132 --> 02:03.834
Her dad being Filipino,

02:03.868 --> 02:05.636
means something.

02:05.670 --> 02:07.438
Okay, you lost me.

02:07.472 --> 02:08.972
Come on.

02:09.007 --> 02:13.377
She's gonna be half
Filipino, half black.

02:13.411 --> 02:16.246
That means she's
gonna be pretty.

02:16.281 --> 02:19.716
She's gonna have
light skin and good hair

02:19.751 --> 02:23.253
and an easier life.

02:23.288 --> 02:24.721
Oh, God...

02:24.756 --> 02:26.757
Please don't lecture me.

02:26.791 --> 02:28.992
Niecy, you're beautiful.

02:29.027 --> 02:30.294
Oh, God.

02:30.328 --> 02:32.396
They would pay good
money for your skin

02:32.430 --> 02:35.833
and your... your eyes,
your smile.

02:35.867 --> 02:38.302
Please, Auntie, you don't
think I know what it means

02:38.336 --> 02:42.606
when people say that I have a
nice smile and nice eyes?

02:42.640 --> 02:46.243
Niecy, you're beautiful.

02:46.277 --> 02:49.813
Ain't no man ever fall for me.

02:49.848 --> 02:53.817
No, but they keep
coming back, don't they?

02:53.852 --> 02:56.286
That's because I put it down.

02:56.321 --> 02:58.388
No, no, don't...
say in the bedroom.

02:58.423 --> 03:02.259
In the bedroom,
in the car, movie theater.

03:02.293 --> 03:05.229
I've probably done things that
you never even heard of,

03:05.263 --> 03:07.831
being honest.
Okay, Niecy, just...

03:07.866 --> 03:10.200
Stop, I... I can't.

03:15.607 --> 03:17.641
You asked me what happened.

03:21.146 --> 03:23.213
Do you really wanna know?

03:27.986 --> 03:33.123
I grew up.

03:33.158 --> 03:37.394
I looked around.

03:37.428 --> 03:42.099
And I was finally
real with myself.

03:42.133 --> 03:45.502
I'm just saying.

03:45.537 --> 03:49.907
I want for my baby to have

03:49.941 --> 03:55.112
every possible opportunity...

03:55.146 --> 04:01.018
Because in this world
pretty is it.

04:01.052 --> 04:04.121
Then look at me.
Oh, baby...

04:04.155 --> 04:06.356
Baby, you are so beautiful.

04:06.391 --> 04:08.859
I wish you knew it.

04:08.893 --> 04:11.595
If you could only see...

04:11.629 --> 04:14.064
You have to say that,
though, you're my Auntie.

04:14.098 --> 04:16.433
No, no.

04:16.466 --> 04:19.570
I'm saying it...

04:19.603 --> 04:22.539
because it's true.

04:22.574 --> 04:23.740
And I love your hair.

04:23.775 --> 04:28.412
It's not mine.
And neither's mine.

04:28.446 --> 04:30.747
Well, I think I'm ready
for my guilt gifts.

04:32.750 --> 04:36.153
Girl, you were ready when my
ass walked through the door.

04:36.187 --> 04:40.123
Oh, baby.

04:40.158 --> 04:42.960
Can you stay the night?

04:42.994 --> 04:44.695
Of course.

